syscall_table[] Function Pointer Array indexed by EAX

Cycle Cost Breakdown per Syscall Round-Trip
SYSENTER uses 3 MSRs CPU registers, no memory read
vDSO: zero-syscall hot paths like clock_gettime
User reg setup EAX=4 EBX=1 ECX EDX
5x CPU push SS ESP EFLAGS CS EIP

DPL=3: ring-3 code CAN execute int 0x80 (else GPF)

Interrupt gate would freeze scheduler during every syscall

div.p: nasm global isr128 isr128: ; Trap gate: IF not cleared push dword 0 ; dummy error code push dword 128 ; vector = 0x80 jmp isr_common_stub

nasm isr_common_stub: pusha ; EAX ECX EDX EBX ESP EBP ESI EDI push ds push es ; push fs ; push gs mov ax, 0x10 ; kernel data segment mov ds, ax ; mov es, ax push esp ; arg: interrupt_frame_t ptr call syscall_dispatch add esp, 4 ; pop gs fs es ds popa add esp, 8 ; discard vector+error_code iret
